            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The Fawara Sanyantra under the Agriculture Department of the Rajasthan government will give 70% to 75% subsidy to the farmers for installing sprinkler plants. Through this farmers can irrigate more land by getting sprinkler subsidy. The subsidy given by the state government to the farmers will be sent directly to their bank accounts through DBT. To avail of the benefit of the Rajasthan Fawara Sanyantra Subsidy Yojana, a farmer should have land up to 0.2 hectares. So that the fields can be irrigated by installing sprinkler plants. The income of farmers will improve through this scheme. Apart from this, efficient utilization and production will also increase. Besides, 50% to 55% of water can be saved by irrigating the fields through sprinklers."
